commit.message: Fix eldoc warnings.

Fix emacs native compilation warning

```
 ■  Warning (comp): pfuture.el:61:2: Warning: docstring has wrong usage
of unescaped single quotes (use \= or different quoting)
 ■  Warning (comp): pfuture.el:123:2: Warning: docstring has wrong usage
of unescaped single quotes (use \= or different quoting)
```

To reproduce, have emacs built with native compilation and notice the
compilation logs. You can then open a file and run `M-x
emacs-lisp-native-compile-and-load` before and after the changes to see the
warning is removed.
Make sure process buffers are hidden.
Make sure stdout buffer is destroyed when future is never awaited.
Fix stderr retrieval.

Collect stdout in a buffer instead of concatenating strings.

Fixes #7
Don't run buffer-list-update-hook for pfuture's buffers.

Use default encoding for process output instead of none.

Fixes #6

Update documentation, include examples, compare with async.el.

Fixes #2

Separate stderr from stdout

* Add a pipe for stderr with make-pipe-process.
* Use a sentinel to delete-process the pipe.
* Allow output from other processes in pfuture-await-to-finish to fix an
  issue with a large number of pfutures resolving simultaneously hitting
  the maximum number of open files.
* Rename 'result to 'stdout, add 'stderr and 'stderr-process to the
  process plist.
Fix define-inline evaluation directive.
Add convenience macro to quick grab callback process' output.
Use inline instead of defsubst.
Simplify name handling, allowing for command to be a symbol.
Handle backquoted commands in callback form.
Eldoc correction.
Update eldoc, add command to quickly grab output from process buffer.
Bind the process buffer under the name `pfuture-buffer`.
Pass the process buffer instead of the output to the callback.
Add parameters for custom buffer and filter function.
Add support for single function call callback forms.
Fix callback expansion for the case that a variable is passed.
Improve handling of callback forms.
Collect process output in a buffer instead if appending it.
Use pcase to check structure of passed functions.
Add missing on-status-change type switch.
Accept functions as well as sexprs, improve documentation.
Add pfuture-callback.
Use a pipe for subprocess communication.
Use a named fuction instead of a lambda.
